    </p>
  </section>

  <style>
    .legal {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      background: #111827;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.35);
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    .legal h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #f9fafb;
    }

    .legal h2 {
